  CTE t1
    ->  Seq Scan on customer  (cost=0.00..32.98 rows=1168 width=4) (actual time=0.074..0.466 rows=584 loops=1)
          Filter: (active = 1)
          Rows Removed by Filter: 15
  CTE t2
