          Group By Key: t1.customer_id
          ->  Hash Join  (cost=37.96..842.59 rows=32119 width=4) (actual time=2.827..9.532 rows=15640 loops=1)
                Hash Cond: (r.customer_id = t1.customer_id)
                ->  Seq Scan on rental r  (cost=0.00..318.72 rows=16472 width=4) (actual time=0.015..1.764 rows=16044 loops=1)
                ->  Hash  (cost=23.36..23.36 rows=1168 width=4) (actual time=1.188..1.188 rows=584 loops=1)
                       Buckets: 32768  Batches: 1  Memory Usage: 277kB
                      ->  CTE Scan on t1  (cost=0.00..23.36 rows=1168 width=4) (actual time=0.085..0.642 rows=584 loops=1)
  ->  Hash Right Join  (cost=369.24..390.95 rows=200 width=44) (actual time=22.831..22.838 rows=10 loops=1)
        Hash Cond: (payment.customer_id = t2.customer_id)
        Filter: (COALESCE((sum(payment.amount)), 0::numeric) > 20::numeric)
